---
layout: layouts/page
title: Notes
description: Notes and thoughts by Ren Hale
---

<article class="h-entry">

  
  <div class="e-content">
    <p>A collection of quick thoughts, ideas, and observations that don't quite warrant a full blog post but are worth capturing.</p>
    
    <div class="notes-grid">
      {% for note in collections.notes %}
      <a href="{{ note.url }}" class="note-card-link">
        <article class="h-entry note-entry">
          <div class="note-icon">
            <img src="/assets/images/notes-icon.svg" alt="Notes icon">
          </div>
          <h3 class="p-name">{{ note.data.title }}</h3>
          <div class="post-meta">
            <time class="dt-published" datetime="{{ note.date | htmlDateString }}">{{ note.date | readableDate }}</time>
          </div>
          <div class="e-content">
            <p>{{ note.data.description }}</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</article>

